<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="minimum-n">minimum <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mɪnɪməm/    美 /'mɪnɪməm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>最低限度；最小量：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We have <strong>a minimum of</strong> 28 people living here in the winter and a maximum of 125 in the summer. 
冬天我们最少有28人住在这里，夏天最多有125人。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>At a minimum</strong>, we must hire three new teachers.
我们最起码应该招三名新教师。</p></div></div>